summary: My initial reaction was that the “Jonah goes full awkward at the mention of having a crush on someone else” scene meant that he...
body:
My initial reaction was that the “Jonah goes full awkward at the mention of having a crush on someone else” scene meant that he already had a crush on someone but after reading the texts–where Andi stresses out to Cyrus about Jonah liking someone–I’m very convinced that this is another fake out. The same way the writers made us believe J*ffy would happen and, to a lesser extent, the same way they tried to make us think that Autumn Festival wish was Jonah’s when it was actually Bowie’s (okay, I should say “is probably Bowie’s” in case I’m very wrong). Ironically, sometimes when they try to push us one way in the text app, it’s a sign that the show itself will go the other.

Jonah is probably just very uncomfortable with the idea of Andi dating someone else, or takes their conversation as Andi saying that she likes someone new…probably a combo of both?
